<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 09:15:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>日本首相因地震风险警告取消中亚和蒙古之行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-pm-cancels-central-asia-mongolia-trip-after-earthquake-risk-warning-2024-08-09/</link><description>日本首相岸田文雄周五取消了本周末访问中亚和蒙古的计划，此前史无前例地发布了太平洋沿岸大地震风险高于平常的警告。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 09:07:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-pm-cancels-central-asia-mongolia-trip-after-earthquake-risk-warning-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>EnBW可能会考虑将中国风力涡轮机用于未来的项目</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/enbw-may-consider-chinese-wind-turbines-future-projects-2024-08-09/</link><description>德国公用事业公司EnBW首席财务官周五表示，该公司正在考虑是否在未来的项目中使用中国风力涡轮机，称西方供应商数量相当少，并指出了潜在的经济效益。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 09:03:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/enbw-may-consider-chinese-wind-turbines-future-projects-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>斐济总理将于8月12日至21日访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fijis-prime-minister-visit-china-aug-12-21-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国外交部周五表示，斐济总理西蒂维尼·拉布卡将于周一至8月21日访问中国，欢迎两国有机会建立战略关系。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 08:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fijis-prime-minister-visit-china-aug-12-21-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国主要港口报告称台湾货船发生爆炸</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/major-chinese-port-reports-blast-cargo-ship-cctv-says-2024-08-09/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，全球最繁忙的港口之一中国宁波舟山港周五报道称，一艘集装箱船上发生爆炸，产生的冲击波在一公里外都能感受到。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 07:30:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/major-chinese-port-reports-blast-cargo-ship-cctv-says-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国7月份银行贷款将下降，北京将重点关注政策支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-bank-lending-set-dip-keeps-beijing-focused-policy-support-2024-08-09/</link><description>路透周五的一项调查显示，尽管央行加大了对经济的政策支持，但受信贷需求不温不火和季节性因素拖累，中国7月份新增人民币贷款可能较上月大幅下降。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 07:17:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-bank-lending-set-dip-keeps-beijing-focused-policy-support-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>随着国内航空公司向海外扩张，外国航空公司对中国失去了兴趣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/foreign-airlines-lose-interest-china-domestic-carriers-expand-abroad-2024-08-09/</link><description>行业数据显示，中国航空公司正在国际航线上获得市场份额，因为中国旅游需求疲软、成本上升以及需要避开俄罗斯领空而导致飞行时间延长，令外国竞争对手望而却步。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 06:56:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/foreign-airlines-lose-interest-china-domestic-carriers-expand-abroad-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国要求一些券商对债券交易进行合规检查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-tells-some-brokerages-conduct-compliance-checks-bond-trading-sources-say-2024-08-09/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，中国证券监管机构已下令一些券商检查其债券交易活动，当局试图遏制对中国政府债券的疯狂购买。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 05:57:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-tells-some-brokerages-conduct-compliance-checks-bond-trading-sources-say-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，字节跳动寻求 50 亿美元贷款再融资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/bytedance-seek-refinancing-5-bln-loan-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-08-09/</link><description>彭博社周五援引知情人士的话报道称，Tiktok 所有者字节跳动正准备在三年内为一笔 50 亿美元的贷款再融资。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 04:23:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/bytedance-seek-refinancing-5-bln-loan-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>从百事可乐到宝洁，印度成为下一个增长大赌注，而中国落后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/pepsico-pg-india-becomes-next-big-growth-bet-china-lags-2024-08-09/</link><description>印度已成为百事可乐、联合利华和其他包装食品巨头的下一个大赌注，这些巨头希望填补中国经济复苏不平衡留下的增长真空。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 03:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/pepsico-pg-india-becomes-next-big-growth-bet-china-lags-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国7月份降雨和洪水导致自然灾害损失近一倍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-rains-floods-led-near-doubling-natural-disaster-losses-july-2024-08-09/</link><description>中国政府表示，7月份中国的极端降雨和严重洪涝导致自然灾害造成的经济损失比去年同期增加近一倍。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 03:20:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-rains-floods-led-near-doubling-natural-disaster-losses-july-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>天气因素导致中国消费价格上涨；国内需求依然疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-consumer-prices-jump-faster-than-expected-producer-deflation-2024-08-09/</link><description>7月份中国消费者价格上涨速度略快于预期，部分原因是天气因素影响了食品供应，而生产者通货紧缩持续存在，使中国的基本消费趋势保持疲软，这是对政策制定者的考验。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 01:37:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-consumer-prices-jump-faster-than-expected-producer-deflation-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称交易账户不得借用，中国国债下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-bond-trading-accounts-must-not-be-borrowed-or-transferred-state-media-2024-08-09/</link><description>监管机构对中国炙手可热的债券市场涉嫌不当行为展开调查后，官方媒体表示交易账户不得借用或转让，中国国债周五下跌。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 00:59:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-bond-trading-accounts-must-not-be-borrowed-or-transferred-state-media-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大和澳大利亚瞄准中国，表示加强军事合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-australia-eyeing-china-signal-more-military-cooperation-2024-08-08/</link><description>加拿大和澳大利亚对中国对南海争议海域的主权声索表示震惊，周四表示，两国将加强军事和国防工业合作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 21:42:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-australia-eyeing-china-signal-more-military-cooperation-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>咖啡贸易商 NKG 进军中国以满足不断增长的需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/coffee-trader-nkg-expands-into-china-tap-surging-demand-2024-08-08/</link><description>全球最大的咖啡贸易商之一、德国咖啡贸易商 Neumann Kaffee Gruppe (NKG) 周四表示，该公司已在中国开设了一家子公司，希望满足亚洲增长最快的咖啡市场对咖啡豆不断增长的需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 21:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/coffee-trader-nkg-expands-into-china-tap-surging-demand-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>举重-中国小将罗夺得女子59公斤级金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/weightlifting-luo-china-wins-womens-59kg-gold-medal-2024-08-08/</link><description>中国小将罗世芳周四在巴黎奥运会上以241公斤的总成绩夺得59公斤级奥运会举重冠军，刷新了抓举和挺举的奥运纪录。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 15:14:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/weightlifting-luo-china-wins-womens-59kg-gold-medal-2024-08-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>